mmap2 takes the offset as some unit of bytes. But what unit?

arc: pagesize (variable)
arm: 4kB
csky: 4kB
hexagon: pagesize (variable)
i386: pagesize (fixed to 4kB)
m68k: pagesize (variable)
microblaze: 4kB
mips: 4kB
nios2: pagesize (fixed to 4kB)
openrisc: pagesize (fixed to 8kB)
parisc: 4kB
powerpc: 4kB
riscv: 4kB
sh: 4kB
sparc: 4kB
